{
  "stem": "17135.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 261.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they knew that this is an official plan concocted by the Gestapo headquarters in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And if they have a chance, they will do that, the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And for some reason, they assigned those three people-- my brother and two of his friends-- one, one his name was Nathan Wiseman, and the other guy's name was Yellick Wasserman.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "One was a medical student, the other was, was a law student.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And what they demanded is they should themself escape and get in touch with the partisan fighters outside, with Polish fighting groups.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And then organize because they know the inside, able to come back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They should disappear.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Nobody should know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They would cover up, which was very difficult to do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But that was the plan.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "In order to get out of the camp, they wanted to make a short in the electricity in the barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And there was a Polish political prisoner, a Polish political prisoner, who was the camp electrician.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And he was part of the conspiracy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "He also wanted to get out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "In the last minute, he went and betrayed the plan to a fellow prisoner, to a Polish doctor who was an anti-semitic bastard.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And he right away went to the Lagerkommandant and told him the story.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "They were arrested.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And then they were tortured for two weeks in the famous torture block in Auschwitz, in block 11.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I was, I was there just a few weeks ago, a few months ago.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when I heard about it, I was very upset.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and, and I-- was very difficult, but I asked my brother, why didn't you tell me about it?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was saying, of course I didn't tell you about it.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
